    AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040011> "An operator role is a role indicating responsibility for operating equipment or systems, typically in a laboratory or manufacturing setting."@en)
    AnnotationAssertion(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/logistics/PMD_0000060> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040011> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean>)
