    AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040110> "planned process in which an algorithm or an encoded algorithm is realized by an agent"@en-us)
    AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000412> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040111> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/Core/ManufacturingProcess>)
    AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040111> "manufacturing process"@en)
    AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040111> "planned process that consists of a structured set of operations through which input material is transformed or modified"@en-us)
    AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000412> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040112> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/Core/AssemblyProcess>)
