    AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040112> "manufacturing process in which a number of material components are physically connected to each other to form an assembly"@en-us)
    AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000412> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040113> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/Core/MaterialLocationChangeProcess>)
