    AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000412> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040114> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/supplychain/SupplyChain/ArrivalProcess>)
