    AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040114> "material location change process that consists of the participating entity reaching its destination such that the travel or transport process which it is a part of is completed"@en-us)
    AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000412> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0040115> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/supplychain/SupplyChain/DepartureProcess>)
